tourBios.exmtStatus: Conditionally Exempt / 77th qualifier from Qualifying Tournament, Money List 61-100
tourBios.carHigh: 2011: Will be a rookie on Tour in 2012. Has yet to play in a PGA TOUR event.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won the Turtle Bay Resort Invitational at UC-Irvine and earned All Big West Conference honors all four years.
tourBios.personal: Biggest thrill outside golf is skydiving...Never travels without his headphones...Always uses a gold ball marker...Favorite websites are youtube.com, twitter.com and PGATOUR.com. Follows the Los Angeles Lakers, New England Patriots, Anaheim Ducks and Anaheim Angels. Favorite movies are "Wedding Crashers," "The Hangover" and "Step Brothers." Listens to the Red Hot Chili Peppers and The Fray...Favorite books are Of Mice and Men. Like to visit Singapore, Los Angeles and Las Vegas. Favorite gadget is his iPad and TaylorMade driver...Twitter account is @seanshahi...Favorite apps are Twitter, Angry Birds and Kayak...Carries Powerbars, Oreos and gum in his golf bag...Not many people know that he use to ski single- and double-black diamond slopes.
tourBios.otherInfo: Played Asian Tour (2009-2010), Canadian Tour (2010-2011) and Tour de las Americas (2010-2011).
